text = scribble("[c_orange]Investors[c_white] will continue in one direction until they reach an obstacle. At many intersections, you'll find [c_teal]shallow waters[c_white]. Click on them to place a Driftwood Blockade. Investors that reach a blockade will change directions. You may only have 4 Blockades at a time. Placing another will remove the oldest.").align(fa_left, fa_top).wrap(256).transform(.8, .8, 0);